# ── Cross-layer connections ─────────────────────────────────────

foundations -> encoding: primitives feed
encoding -> structure: type system enables
structure -> ladder: grammar maps to

ladder -> connections.gdgm: tier ladder mirrors cosmological arc {
  style: {stroke-dash: 5; stroke: "#3498db"}
}

problems.bridge -> connections.ivna: unformalized bridge {
  style: {stroke-dash: 5; stroke: "#e74c3c"}
}

connections.lang -> encoding: reverse-engineering epistemology {
  style: {stroke-dash: 5; stroke: "#3498db"}
}

connections.lean -> structure: formalize unique parse (P1) {
  style: {stroke-dash: 5; stroke: "#3498db"}
}

structure -> problems: unresolved at this layer {
  style: {stroke-dash: 3; stroke: "#e74c3c"}
}

# ── Core Insight ────────────────────────────────────────────────

insight: |md
  **Core Insight**: `0` individuates by surrounding existence with nothing.
  Without `0`, existence (`1`) is unbounded and universal.
  All meaning emerges from string structure — nesting is the only operator.
| {
  near: bottom-center
  style: {
    fill: "#0f3460"
    stroke: "#e94560"
    font-color: "#e0e0e0"
    border-radius: 8
  }
}
